Official Page of Montauk Brewing Company + Montauk Hard Seltzer - Must be 21+ to follow.
“Come As You Are”

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company.

node.text: Thank you to all of our fans for your incredible support through the years! This 9 Year Anniversary surfboard from @faktionsurfboards filled up quickly. 10 Year planning starts now! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Cycle Sauce IPA is back and available fresh off the canning line this Wednesday! Brewed with Idaho 7 and Cascade hops and clocking in at 6.2% ABV, this beer is a great choice to celebrate a long ride, or really to celebrate anything worth celebrating. See you at noon this Wednesday! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Navy Beach, Montauk. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text: Montauk Hard Seltzer felt like a good move today. Maybe you’re in a beer mood though. The good news is now you don’t need to pick sides. @montaukbrewco beer or hard seltzer - the choice is yours. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Hot and humid with a 100% chance of cold beers. Patio Vibes are strong, to quite strong right now! Thanks to all of our fans for celebrating with @montaukbrewco #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Montauk Brewing Co. on July 15, 2021 tagging @jjamet. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Join us next Thursday at noon for a very special re-release of one of our most popular Ocean Series beers - Cycle Sauce IPA! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Montauk Brewing Co. on July 14, 2021 tagging @whalebonemagazine. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'AmishToyBox.com'.

node.text: You’re almost through Wednesday, and that’s really good news. Maybe there’s a cold @montaukbrewco in your future because hey, you’ve earned it! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'MONTAUK BREWING co.'.

node.text: Stay tuned for some fresh new brews coming soon from @montaukbrewco World HQ. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on July 11, 2021. May be an image of twilight, ocean, sky and nature.

node.text: There’s a spot in Montauk that’s right in between a little pond and a big lake that’s a good place to catch sunset. It also happens to be a good place to enjoy a cold beer after an evening bike ride. Hope some of you are enjoying an ice cold @montaukbrewco at your favorite spot! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink, outdoors and text that says 'MONTAUK BREWING co.'.

node.text: Easy Riser is our take on a Belgian-Style Wheat Ale. Mellow and easy going, like a gently rising wave as it approaches the shore, this brew is the perfect expression of the Montauk Vibe - embodying the pure, relaxed enjoyment of the No-Frills Good Life. Brewed with coriander and orange peel, Easy Riser Belgian White is incredibly smooth and, as the name suggests, incredibly easy to love. Have you tried Easy Riser yet? #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Montauk Brewing Co. on July 10, 2021 tagging @lacolombecoffee. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Yesterday right before we opened at noon, the rain stopped and the sun popped out. What happened next was that fun was had and hi-fives were exchanged. There were fresh beers, cold hard seltzers, delicious pizza, tasty ice cream and cold brew coffee. Now that’s the way to kick off summer. Thanks to everyone who came down to the patio and shared in the good times! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on July 08, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: 100 Great Days is a thing we created to celebrate the 100 Great Days between Memorial Day and Labor Day. The goal is to pack as much fun, smiles, hi-fives, Montauk beer and hard seltzer into those 100 days as possible - the countdown has begun. Link in bio for your chance to win some pretty amazing prizes! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of twilight, nature and ocean.

node.text: Sending you good vibes from Montauk. Maybe enjoy a couple of cold @montaukbrewco beers later, just a thought. #montauk #comeasyouare
